      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLORAL LEGEND (4) produced a good effort last start when third over 1000m at Dalby to make it four minor placings from eight runs this preparation. Has good early toe so she should be handy in the run. Will give a great sight. SILVERTURN (7) remains a maiden after seven runs. Was well in commission last time but could only manage to finish sixth over 950m at Cairns. Finds a suitable assignment this time and is a great chance to break through. HEEZ DE MAN (1) returns from a spell of seven months and is having his first run for a new yard. Finished sixth at Mornington over 1200m when first-up last time in work. Can measure up at the first run for a new barn. MIDDLE CHILD (5) was solidly backed last time out but failed to fire and finished eighth over 1000m at Townsville, beaten 6 lengths. Looks close to a win and worth including.",
